### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE Drug_Interactions (
    drug_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    drug_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    effect_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Adverse_Effects (
    effect_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    effect_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    severity ENUM('Mild', 'Moderate', 'Severe'),
    affected_population TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Drug_Effects (
    drug_id INT,
    effect_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (drug_id, effect_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (drug_id) REFERENCES Drug_Interactions(drug_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (effect_id) REFERENCES Adverse_Effects(effect_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Patient_Drug_History (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    drug_id INT,
    dosage INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (drug_id) REFERENCES Drug_Interactions(drug_id)
);
